credit.credit-words: Music: Oliver Holden (1765–1844) Text: Douglas Wilson, 2005
3. At this white table, wine and bread Will weave us now into the Head, As we grow to a perfect man And there fulfill salvation’s plan.
4. The Lord has spoken living words, He gave us ears, and thus we heard. We will not give our sons a stone, We will not live by bread alone.
